heading: Wind septets.
general-note: Here are entered collections of septets not in a specific form or of a specific type for various combinations of seven woodwind and brass instruments. Individual wind septets and collections not in a specific form or of a specific type for a single combination of instruments are entered under this heading followed by a parenthetical qualifier with the instruments in alphabetical order..
Compositions for seven brass instruments are entered under. Brass septets;. compositions for seven woodwind instruments are entered under. Woodwind septets..
